Citation.sTitle: Solubility of Thiotriazinone in Ethanol, 1-Propanol, 2-Propanol, 1-Butanol, Acetonitrile, Acetone, Ethyl Acetate, and Water from 293 K to 343 K
Citation.sAbstract: The solubility of thiotriazinone in ethanol, 1-propanol, 2-propanol, 1-butanol, acetonitrile, acetone, ethyl acetate, and water was measured using a laser technique with a temperature range from 293.65 K to 343.70 K. The results of these measurements were correlated with a semiempirical equation. The calculated results of which are proved to show fine representation of experimental data.
